n. We also collect information if you contact our customer service department.\r\n\r\nWe collect information from you passively. For example, we use tracking tools like browser cookies.\r\n\r\nWe get information about you from third parties. For example, our business partners may give us information about you. Social media platforms may also provide information about you.\r\n\r\n<u>WE USE INFORMATION AS WE DESCRIBE.</u>\r\n\r\nWe use information to improve our understanding of your interests and concerns. We may get your information to make <a href="http://www.haraandco.com">www.majorcraft-america.com</a> better. We may use your information to customize your experience and to tailor our marketing activities to fit your needs and interests. We may combine information we get from you with information about you that we receive from third parties.\r\n\r\nWe use information to respond to your requests or questions. We may use your information to answer your questions or provide information you request.\r\n\r\nWe use information for security purposes. We may use information to protect our company, our customers, our employees, and the <a href="http://www.haraandco.com">www.majorcraft-america.com</a> website and app. We also use information to collect and enforce accounts and to prevent fraud.\r\n\r\nWe use information for marketing purposes. There may be third party offers or products that you may find interesting. We may call you, or send you emails or text messages. We may use other means as they arise. We may also use push notifications on our mobile app.\r\n\r\nWe use information to communicate with you about your account or our relationship. We may contact you about changes to the <a href="http://www.haraandco.com">www.majorcraft-america.com</a> website and app, or regarding service updates. We may also contact you about feedback or about this privacy policy or our terms of use.\r\n\r\nAdditionally, we use information to maintain transaction and other business records. We will do so for as long as necessary. We also use information for internal purposes. This includes administrative and audit purposes. We also use information to meet legal, insurance and processing requirements. We will also use information as otherwise allowed by law, including if we have notified you. We will seek your permission if we are legally required to do so.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<u>WE MAY SHARE INFORMATION WITH THIRD PARTIES.</u>\r\n\r\nWe will share information with third parties who perform services on our behalf. For example, we share information with vendors who send emails for us. We may also share personal information with service providers that help us operate the <a href="http://www.haraandco.com">www.majorcraft-america.com</a> website and app, or run promotions.\r\n\r\nWe may share your information with our parent and affiliated companies for various reasons including internal audits, management, billing or administrative purposes. This includes future subsidiaries or affiliates.\r\n\r\nWe may share information with our business partners. For example, we will share information with third parties who jointly sponsor an event or promotions with us.\r\n\r\nIf we merge with another company, or part or all of our business or assets are transferred, assigned or sold to another company, we may share your information with that company. Your personal information will be disclosed to our successor or assign in these circumstances that can use and disclose your information for substantially the same purposes as set out in this privacy policy.\r\n\r\nWe will disclose your information if we think we must to comply with the law or to protect ourselves. This includes compliance with laws outside of the United States that may apply to us. We may share the information if a government agency or investigative body requests. We may share information when we are investigating potential fraud. This may include fraud during a sweepstakes or promotion.\r\n\r\n<u>YOU