d security measures, the Internet is not 100 percent secure. We cannot guarantee that any of your personal information stored or sent to us will be completely safe. We encourage you to use caution when using the Internet.\r\n\r\n<u>WE MAY LINK TO THIRD PARTY SITES OR SERVICES THAT WE DO NOT CONTROL.</u>\r\n\r\nYou may be able to access certain third party sites from <a href="http://www.haraandco.com">www.majorcraft-america.com</a> or the app. This includes social media sites. This privacy policy does not apply to those third party sites. We advise you to check the privacy policies of all third party sites you visit to find out how they handle your personal information. We are not responsible for those third party websites.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<u>WE STORE INFORMATION IN AND OUTSIDE OF THE UNITED STATES.</u>\r\n\r\nInformation that we or our vendors maintain may be stored, processed or accessed both within and outside of the United States. You understand and agree that we may transfer your information to the United States or elsewhere and that the laws of these countries may not afford the same level of protection as those in our country. <a href="http://www.haraandco.com">www.majorcraft-america.com</a> is subject to United States law.\r\n\r\n<u>WE MAY UPDATE THIS PRIVACY POLICY.</u>\r\n\r\nWe will notify you of any material changes as required by law. We will post an updated copy of our website. Please check this page for updates.\r\n\r\n<u>TRACKING</u>\r\n\r\nYou can control tracking tools. Most Internet browsers give you the ability to control cookies. How you control cookies depends on the type of cookies. Some browsers can be set to reject browser cookies. If you block cookies on your browser, certain features on <a href="http://www.haraandco.com">www.majorcraft-america.com</a> may not work.\r\n\r\n<u>PLEASE CONTACT US IF YOU HAVE ANY QUESTIONS.</u>\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions, you may write us an email us at info@majorcraft-america.com.', 'Terms and Conditions', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'terms-and-conditions', '', '', '2016-01-13 09:14:07', '2016-01-13 17:14:07', '', 0, 'http://majorcraft.vmsrv16.inside.cactussoft.biz/?page_id=419', 0, 'page', '', 0),
