(536, 1, '2016-01-12 14:59:35', '2016-01-12 14:59:35', 'Cutting-edge ""NANOALLOY"" technology\r\nnext-generation bass rod SPEEDSTYLE Debut!\r\nNANOALLOY technology gives the rod its stiffness and helps to reduced rod weight.  It also increases the performance of the blank.  We achieved high sensitivity to feel even the slightest bite. Hooking power and lifting power are unparalleled.  We adopted a suitable guide setting and grip design to get the best from each of the models.  \r\nQuickly catch bass with SPEEDSTYLE!\r\n\r\nDue to our manufacturing of the rods being produced manually, processes such as adhesion at the time of parts assembly, epoxy coating, and the painting process can be affected.', 'Speedstyle - Spinning', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'speedstyle-spinning', '', '', '2016-01-12 15:01:18', '2016-01-12 23:01:18', '', 0, 'http://majorcraft.vmsrv16.inside.cactussoft.biz/?post_type=product&#038;p=536', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(537, 1, '2016-01-12 15:01:24', '2016-01-12 15:01:24', '10 years have already passed since our smashing debut.  The legendary ""Major Stick (MS)"" was redesigned based on Major Craft''s 10 years experience and data to give you the ""MS-X"" debut.\r\nTo make it work over the next decade, we focused on everything (blank, guides, reel seat,  etc.) and adopted  the highest level of leading-edge spec.  We reinforced the stiffness against torsion by putting the new process of manufacturing the ""Cross Force Plus"" on the butt section, which is made by double taping the cross force on flat woven carbon and screwing it tight to the Cross Force on the belly part.  And we adopted all titunium frames guides.  Then we achieved the advancement of the level for crisp high-end action, stiffness, sensitivity and lightweight properties.  This amazing spec exceeds everything.  X means 10 years.  We want you to experience the high potential which live up to the name.\r\n\r\nDue to our manufacturing of the rods being produced manually, processes such as adhesion at the time of parts assembly, epoxy coating, and the painting process can be affected.', 'MS-X - Casting', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ms-x-casting', '', '', '2016-01-12 16:47:15', '2016-01-12 16:47:15', '', 0, 'http://majorcraft.vmsrv16.inside.cactussoft.biz/?post_type=product&#038;p=537', 0, 'product', '', 0),
